title: CNBC presents Crime Inc. - Deadly Prescriptions (2011) HDTV
description:
-About Crime Inc.: Deadly Prescriptions-

It's America's secret epidemic. The illegal use of prescription drugs is big business for unscrupulous dealers and doctors around the country. Sales of prescription drugs topped $300 billion in 2010, and criminals are doing everything they can to get a piece of it. Between bribed medical professionals and online rogue pharmacies, potent prescription medicine is falling into the wrong hands.
